    {
      "_type": "text",
      "contents": "\n\n(** We want to have the following as subdirectories/modules, not at top level.  Unfortunately, namespacing in Coq is kind-of broken (see, e.g., https://coq.inria.fr/bugs/show_bug.cgi?id=3676), so we don't get the ability to rename subfolders by [Including] into other modules. *)\n"
